&lt;html&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hi, my name is Derek Caramella.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;square&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div&gt;
        &lt;img src=&#34;https://derekcaramella.github.io/Data-Science-Portfolio/images/Derek_Presenting.png&#34; alt=&#34;Personal Picture&#34; width=360&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am a Digitization Lead for pladis Global, a chocolate manufacturing company. I deliver data visualizations to empower
objective decision making to ensure effective operation. I use python, visual basic, SQL, and Excel technologies to build local
dashboards on servers and deliever statistical insight to reduce deadweigh losses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I graduate from Elmira College, in May 2021 as a triple major in Business Administration, Economics, &amp; Political 
Science with a concentration in Public Affairs. Following graduation, I will attend the University of Rochester striving
for my Master&#39;s in Data Science.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;square&#34; style=&#34;float: right&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div&gt;
        &lt;img src=&#34;https://derekcaramella.github.io/Data-Science-Portfolio/images/Lexi_Derek.JPG&#34; alt=&#34;Lexi &amp; Derek&#34; width=300&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outside the workplace &amp; academia, I enjoy playing soccer and spending time outdoors. I have a loving, 
supportive girlfriend that I spend the lion&#39;s share of my recreational time with - we ski, kayak, hike, and 
enjoy life together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you for visiting my portfolio, make sure to network with me if you have any questions or comments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://derekcaramella.github.io/Data-Science-Portfolio/images/Warm_Regards.JPG&#34; alt=&#34;Warm Regards&#34; class=&#34;center&#34; height:20 style=&#34;float: none;&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Warm regards,&lt;br&gt;Derek&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</description>
